{"tid":1698053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果11.8和你返工都推唔郁 更加唔好講全港三罷","createTime":"2019-11-07T08:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T14:43:45.000Z","uid":77393,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7b998d215fe3b96c0f8c21c01d3a8ec6f953736a","tid":1698053,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MgpuwOx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgpuwOx.jpg&h=11494823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家平時口口聲聲話攬炒 心底裏亦都明白三罷係最直接手段 但實行起上嚟要從長計議 的確需時部署同宣傳<br />\n<br />\n而和你返工只需要你比平時返工早多少少起身 基本上都屬於和平抗爭 完咗又可以繼續返工做港豬 其實對大家影響真係唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但以上次經驗 連班黑警都睇死你 直頭布防都唔需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於三罷已經籌備中 今次作為前哨戰 係一個最直接了解三罷可能性嘅機會 所以極需要大家去參與!<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔好俾咁多藉口自己喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者同返工時間唔吻合<br />\n或者地點有距離<br />\n或者早起身真係好難<br />\n<br />\n但如果你連參與嘅意願都冇 就代表你對革命成功嘅渴求其實唔高 場革命就真真正正咁輸喺自己手上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建議活動目標:<br />\n1. 點人數<br />\n不論中途插入或者提早離開 最緊要參與<br />\n<br />\n2. 佔路 影響交通<br />\n唔需要強行佔路 要適當評估環境情況 即使細微影響亦絕對稱得上成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望聽日見到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">切記準時！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"33349a1c00a1790cb802887b8b90b08f64e5b0ab","tid":1698053,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bvCTcoV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbvCTcoV.jpg&h=87c59ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JWXE34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JWXE34.jpg&h=9d8ce577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7rQfCq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7rQfCq.jpg&h=dfa0a304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[重新整合]11.10 7區開花！ 11.11全港3罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樽頸突破！11 11 黎明行動 7:00 18區集合 行動強制罷工！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696996\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696996</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b12eb3f7e73a9413363dacba7623f879960a700b","tid":1698053,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:54:56.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"fe64c8f9edd12b41c7eef341ebd9ae3cbbe0035f","tid":1698053,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"9cb4756b791d87eaadfdf1e7f97802539b3a3d4e","tid":1698053,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"99077eeb7d4a762e496811971e9c98b177b0753d","tid":1698053,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:56:00.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"a9ffdcf782ec7fcf5f14d7110ac383a9cabe2c4a","tid":1698053,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:56:11.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"d1886232f58f28548026a8c9dad02161e1988641","tid":1698053,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:56:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdd152f0475498c002cefbbf14cc4576f6241d4f","tid":1698053,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"大家早睡早起<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6725245c21e90b50955c4eba318db74192396884","tid":1698053,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":